articles.title: State Department issues 'worldwide caution' alert for Americans overseas - Fox News
articles.description: The State Department urged Americans abroad to exercise increased caution, citing the potential for "terrorist attacks" and other violent actions.

Americans traveling abroad are being urged to exercise caution worldwide, the State Department said Friday.
